<section id="integrations" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Agent Integrations</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Practical wiring: binary collector to agent output, OTel time-axis join, and ready connector paths for Claude and Codex.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-2 integration-grid">
      <div class="card integration-card">
        <h3 class="integration-title">1) Binary To Agent Stream</h3>
        <p class="integration-desc">
          Send one semantic JSON object per line from your agent to stdout, then pipe directly into MOVA Compact.
        </p>
        <pre><code>{`python my_agent.py | mova-compact collect --run-dir runs/agent --run-id agent-001 --input -
mova-compact expand --run-dir runs/agent`}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card integration-card">
        <h3 class="integration-title">2) OTel Time Axis Join</h3>
        <p class="integration-desc">
          Export OTel-derived time journal to JSONL and join it with the semantic compact run.
        </p>
        <pre><code>{`python export_otel_jsonl.py --service my-agent --out otel_time.jsonl
mova-compact join --run-dir runs/agent --time otel_time.jsonl
mova-compact verify --run-dir runs/agent`}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card integration-card">
        <h3 class="integration-title">3) Claude Connector</h3>
        <p class="integration-desc">
          Wrapper-first adapter for Anthropic flows and Claude-like events.
        </p>
        <pre><code>{`python connectors/anthropic/anthropic_connector_demo.py | mova-compact collect --run-dir runs/claude --run-id claude-001 --input -
mova-compact expand --run-dir runs/claude`}</code></pre>
        <a href="https://github.com/mova-compact/mova/tree/main/connectors/anthropic" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="integration-link">
          Open Claude Connector
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card integration-card">
        <h3 class="integration-title">4) Codex / OpenAI Connector</h3>
        <p class="integration-desc">
          Adapter for OpenAI/Codex-style tool events with the same collector contract.
        </p>
        <pre><code>{`python connectors/openai/openai_connector_demo.py | mova-compact collect --run-dir runs/codex --run-id codex-001 --input -
mova-compact expand --run-dir runs/codex`}</code></pre>
        <a href="https://github.com/mova-compact/mova/tree/main/connectors/openai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="integration-link">
          Open Codex/OpenAI Connector
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

